      • generateBoard

        public static Path[] generateBoard()

        Generates the Board (of Paths). A path can be generated with left and right nodes (path1 and path2) or none.

        Note: the Path has to be generated from the End of the Board to the Start

        Link to UML
        Returns:
        array with length 2 where index 0 = Starting Career Path, index 1 = Starting College Path
